":"A group of friends attempt to escape the city after an outbreak of demon-possessions. The friends seek shelter in an abandoned church, but their plans for escape are ruined when one of them becomes possessed."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Врата плоти","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Весь мир неожиданно накрывает Апокалипсис, и он выглядит совсем не так, как прогнозировали в разных вариантах. Люди просто начинают превращаться в «зловещих мертвецов», которые уверяют, что они – демоны, которым стало позволено расправиться с человечеством. Группа молодых людей пытаются укрыться от опасности в просторном зале церкви. Но, кажется, спасения нет нигде."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"بوابات الجسد","runtime":91,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://uproarpictures.com/2022/06/30/gates-of-flesh/","overview":"تحاول مجموعة من الأصدقاء الهروب من المدينة بعد انتشار حالات تلبّس بالشياطين. ويلجأ الأصدقاء إلى كنيسة مهجورة طلبًا للملجأ، لكن خططهم للهروب تنهار عندما يُصاب أحدهم بالتلبّس."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Portões do Inferno","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Um grupo de amigos tenta escapar de uma cidade afetada por um surto de possessões demoníacas. Eles procuram refúgio em uma igreja abandonada, mas seus planos são arruinados quando um deles é possuído."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Las Puertas del Infierno","runtime":91,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un grupo de amigos intenta escapar de la ciudad después de un brote de posesiones demoníacas. Los amigos buscan refugio en una iglesia abandonada, pero sus planes de escape se arruinan cuando uno de ellos se vuelve poseído."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"血肉之门","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一群朋友在恶魔附身事件后试图逃离城市。朋友们在一座废弃教堂中寻求庇护，但当其中一人被附身时，他们的逃亡计划被破坏。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[{"id":74,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"Ray Ferrier is a divorced dockworker and less-than-perfect father. Soon after his ex-wife and her new husband drop off his teenage son and young daughter for a rare weekend visit, a strange and powerful lightning storm touches down.","genre_ids":[12,53,878],"popularity":8.8816,"vote_count":8977,"poster_path":"/6Biy7R9LfumYshur3YKhpj56MpB.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-28","vote_average":6.531,"backdrop_path":"/bInicBgSHfQiWLbnRT5jxw9Grvm.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":1977,"adult":false,"title":"The Grudge 3","video":false,"overview":"Jake Kimble, the sole survivor of the Chicago massacre, is killed while in solitary confinement. His doctor begins investigating the claims he made about a long-haired woman in white, as a mysterious Japanese woman arrives at his old apartment building to help them get rid of the curse.","genre_ids":[9648,27,53],"popularity":1.9059,"vote_count":650,"poster_path":"/uEOWWRr8BbgPM0BiJiSTwHGaRx4.jpg","release_date":"2009-05-12","vote_average":5.442,"backdrop_path":"/e3fp9XMQ13b0OCKw9gR3h7ZYoaw.jpg","original_title":"The Grudge 3","original_language":"en"},{"id":280002,"adult":false,"title":"The Remaining","video":false,"overview":"When a group of close-knit friends assemble for the marriage of Skylar and Dan, they have no idea they will witness The Rapture and face a series of catastrophic events turning the celebration into a life-or-death struggle.","genre_ids":[53,27],"popularity":3.8044,"vote_count":486,"poster_path":"/fFeTfXI67Oj80s65jtbq4uQ4InP.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-25","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/lcR8o5Fqm5WfqWkldyV2ZPSqdp8.jpg","original_title":"The Remaining","original_language":"en"},{"id":280016,"adult":false,"title":"Asmodexia","video":false,"overview":"Eloy de Palma is an exorcist pastor roaming the darkest corners of the country with his granddaughter Alba. Their mission is to help those possessed by The Evil One, an infection of the soul that is spreading fast. Each exorcism is tougher than the one before, and every battle reveals a piece of Alba’s forgotten past – an enigma that if unconcealed could change the world as we know it.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":0.2631,"vote_count":37,"poster_path":"/m9rhEvc1FvU1EnEkOgxEGF8W4YJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-19","vote_average":4.622,"backdrop_path":"/AgI5J7wd3NY606u16hk00FiorXL.jpg","original_title":"Asmodexia","original_language":"es"},{"id":1069108,"adult":false,"title":"Microwave Coven","video":false,"overview":"After buying a microwave from a peculiar woman, two college roommates discover their new appliance is not quite what it seems.","genre_ids":[35,27,14],"popularity":0.5549,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/oXC0suIkn6GiyDaBj7h0AUzunKA.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-27","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Microwave Coven","original_language":"en"},{"id":664574,"adult":false,"title":"Silent Night","video":false,"overview":"Nell, Simon, and their boy Art are ready to welcome friends and family for what promises to be a perfect Christmas gathering. Perfect except for one thing: everyone is going to die.","genre_ids":[35,878,27],"popularity":1.677,"vote_count":584,"poster_path":"/bfUO1SBTfgcK77em3lOuRFY2uLc.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-03","vote_average":5.923,"backdrop_path":"/nJYAAOk74VjPlwz34jWFh8MPw2r.jpg","original_title":"Silent Night","original_language":"en"},{"id":474104,"adult":false,"title":"Demon House","video":false,"overview":"Mass hysteria breaks-out over an alleged demonic possession in an Indiana home. Zak Bagans then buys the house, sight unseen, over the phone. He and his crew soon become the next victims of the most documented case of demonic possession in US history.","genre_ids":[99,27,9648,53],"popularity":0.3485,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/80gFuW9wIeKEaswSspSGjSEOcDE.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-01","vote_average":5.333,"backdrop_path":"/fZEVyHIKdLzDFC29W6JCeaJwvUz.jpg","original_title":"Demon House","original_language":"en"},{"id":10722,"adult":false,"title":"The Day of the Beast","video":false,"overview":"When a rogue priest discovers the exact date the Antichrist will be born, he enlists a Death Metal record store clerk and a cheesy TV psychic for an urban spree of gore, sacrilege and twisted humor to prevent the Apocalypse.","genre_ids":[27,35,28],"popularity":1.083,"vote_count":594,"poster_path":"/yEXhgACPIV4PmTgHT2HS3Ko2oS3.jpg","release_date":"1995-10-20","vote_average":7.244,"backdrop_path":"/ijBx6WyNU94rKKmt1iTkD9N1ujn.jpg","original_title":"El día de la bestia","original_language":"es"},{"id":854765,"adult":false,"title":"Witches of Blackwood","video":false,"overview":"When Claire returns to her hometown, she discovers her former home riddled with terrifying witchcraft, the town in the grip of fear, decay, and madness.","genre_ids":[53,27],"popularity":1.6354,"vote_count":52,"poster_path":"/nC5Vlvy1HcVODs87gllNHoyqIhO.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-18","vote_average":6.462,"backdrop_path":"/lEOre2UI2pXPqUhppXgQTcXlZQN.jpg","original_title":"The Unlit","original_language":"en"},{"id":1063882,"adult":false,"title":"Alive","video":false,"overview":"Helen navigates a ravaged world with her boyfriend Kevin and her little brother Barney. Desperate to find help after Barney's infection slowly turns him into a zombie, they come upon a house where lives Dan, a man harboring a heavy secret.","genre_ids":[27,18],"popularity":0.4323,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/mzZOUDYaeeq9rGElNRQaqjMMLXS.jpg","release_date":"2023-01-31","vote_average":2.5,"backdrop_path":"/7RzJTVttQkj9Ehm7J5qBxeUraHu.jpg","original_title":"Alive","original_language":"en"},{"id":4457,"adult":false,"title":"Witchery","video":false,"overview":"A student and her photographer boyfriend visit an island off of Massachusetts to research a hotel supposedly haunted by a witch.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":0.7058,"vote_count":84,"poster_path":"/mCcAeP1Vqz8KkPlKMcceJbqV8Ud.jpg","release_date":"1988-12-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/wsu3LmI11VEwWsooN0v7zY1u3sI.jpg","original_title":"La casa 4","original_language":"en"},{"id":805,"adult":false,"title":"Rosemary's Baby","video":false,"overview":"A young couple, Rosemary and Guy, moves into an infamous New York apartment building, known by frightening legends and mysterious events, with the purpose of starting a family.","genre_ids":[18,27,53],"popularity":3.0772,"vote_count":4282,"poster_path":"/uYgvlHceRFjAFbsNeMInYcLZLUb.jpg","release_date":"1968-06-12","vote_average":7.82,"backdrop_path":"/qszuXKhzYR24oRpsmh7eZaPbvL8.jpg","original_title":"Rosemary's Baby","original_language":"en"},{"id":871,"adult":false,"title":"Planet of the Apes","video":false,"overview":"Astronaut Taylor crash lands on a distant planet ruled by apes who use a primitive race of humans for experimentation and sport. Soon Taylor finds himself among the hunted, his life in the hands of a benevolent chimpanzee scientist.","genre_ids":[878,12,18,28],"popularity":7.0102,"vote_count":3855,"poster_path":"/2r9iKnlSYEk4daQadsXfcjHfIjQ.jpg","release_date":"1968-02-07","vote_average":7.645,"backdrop_path":"/gmJOXle5QeOOVFEYOVBOkmIJUWV.jpg","original_title":"Planet of the Apes","original_language":"en"},{"id":272692,"adult":false,"title":"The Possession of Michael King","video":false,"overview":"The film tells the story of documentary filmmaker Michael King (Shane Johnson), who doesn’t believe in God or the Devil. Following the sudden death of his wife, Michael decides to make his next film about the search for the existence of the supernatural, making himself the center of the experiment – allowing demonologists, necromancers, and various practitioners of the occult to try the deepest and darkest spells and rituals they can find on him – in the hopes that when they fail, he’ll once and for all have proof that religion, spiritualism, and the paranormal are nothing more than myth. But something does happen. An evil and horrifying force has taken over Michael King. And it will not let him go.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":0.796,"vote_count":425,"poster_path":"/r1LrvbUsQHn8ByJIOoeI76F6jR0.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-14","vote_average":6.127,"backdrop_path":"/llGQkZIxoMtSs1IeE3X7y4W696P.jpg","original_title":"The Possession of Michael King","original_language":"en"},{"id":1487,"adult":false,"title":"Hellboy","video":false,"overview":"In the final days of World War II, the Nazis attempt to use black magic to aid their dying cause. The Allies raid the camp where the ceremony is taking place, but not before they summon a baby demon who is rescued by Allied forces and dubbed \"Hellboy\". Sixty years later, Hellboy serves the cause of good rather than evil as an agent in the Bureau of Paranormal Research & Defense, along with Abe Sapien - a merman with psychic powers, and Liz Sherman - a woman with pyrokinesis, protecting America against dark forces.","genre_ids":[14,28],"popularity":5.6077,"vote_count":7293,"poster_path":"/lbaTEneOofwvAyg77R8HbFML2zT.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-02","vote_average":6.676,"backdrop_path":"/avwEj8wiywFH6FZ6h2wzvyJpiH7.jpg","original_title":"Hellboy","original_language":"en"},{"id":1411,"adult":false,"title":"The Rapture","video":false,"overview":"A lonely telephone operator leading an empty, amoral life finds God – only to have her faith continually tested in ways beyond what she could have imagined.","genre_ids":[9648,18,14,53],"popularity":1.0472,"vote_count":92,"poster_path":"/4EkFm13ecqO0eszr7OKT8vf1YjJ.jpg","release_date":"1991-10-04","vote_average":5.723,"backdrop_path":"/ylXFsNIhzq8A5nEqLhPdDYPOnVo.jpg","original_title":"The Rapture","original_language":"en"},{"id":465177,"adult":false,"title":"Berserkers","video":false,"overview":"The film follows Zeke (Robert McMurray), Callie (Alicia Marie Marcucci), Les (Seth Gontkovic) and Hunter (Jake Mulliken) on the eve of Hunter's 29th birthday as they share in a few drinks on a seemingly dull day in their hometown of Somerset. The day takes a turn for the worse as everyone they have ever known are suddenly transformed into aggressively murderous flesh eating freaks. The four comrades are forced to hack and slash their way through the reanimated corpses of their closest friends and loved ones, only to find themselves on the precipice of a post apocalyptic wasteland littered with monsters and the looming threat of their fellow survivors.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":1.4129,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/xRtyCI1AcI2igXC0rX2pzm0j1b5.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-16","vote_average":3.3,"backdrop_path":"/4CKWB9SHod2ezNaNlw2jnb9ZNnB.jpg","original_title":"Meltdown","original_language":"en"},{"id":764,"adult":false,"title":"The Evil Dead","video":false,"overview":"In 1979, a group of college students find a Sumerian Book of the Dead in an old wilderness cabin they've rented for a weekend getaway.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":5.77,"vote_count":4372,"poster_path":"/54C1qdaiSijIU5NeNb4WsPJdNkG.jpg","release_date":"1981-10-15","vote_average":7.275,"backdrop_path":"/onq6lsJLX8ay5iwxEbKX3qJKeO9.jpg","original_title":"The Evil Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":274855,"adult":false,"title":"Geostorm","video":false,"overview":"After an unprecedented series of natural disasters threatened the planet, the world's leaders came together to create an intricate network of satellites to control the global climate and keep everyone safe. But now, something has gone wrong: the system built to protect Earth is attacking it, and it becomes a race against the clock to uncover the real threat before a worldwide geostorm wipes out everything and everyone along with it.","genre_ids":[28,878,53],"popularity":7.0646,"vote_count":5072,"poster_path":"/nrsx0jEaBgXq4PWo7SooSnYJTv.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-12","vote_average":6.111,"backdrop_path":"/vIEuJiIZN9EclAJDmD49F2zUzuX.jpg","original_title":"Geostorm","original_language":"en"},{"id":274899,"adult":false,"title":"Inner Demons","video":false,"overview":"INNER DEMONS follows an 'Intervention'-style reality show crew that films an episode about a sixteen-year old girl, a former A-student, who is fighting addiction but may in fact be suffering from something even more destructive: demonic possession. The movie is an inquiry into the truth about her - with symptoms that straddle the disturbing and scary intersection between insanity, addiction and true possession.","genre_ids":[53,27,9648],"popularity":0.2815,"vote_count":75,"poster_path":"/cnZAp5ZmVbPa6arsQ8VmY02QYli.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-13","vote_average":5.24,"backdrop_path":"/opo0CKGalp6vnM7UeNofw9MqBib.jpg","original_title":"Inner Demons","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt9387532","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148235,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-01-14T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"14"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"US","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"en","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-04-08T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]}],"aggregate_credits":null,"original_network":null,"screenwriters":null,"based_on":null,"filming_location":null,"narrative_location":null,"review_score_rt":null,"review_score_mc":null,"box_office":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"collection_id":null,"wikidata_metadata":{},"mood_tags":null,"trope_tags":null,"vibe